## Client Deployment

The client is a single HTML file with no dependencies. It can be deployed:

- As a static site on any host
- Via Lovable.dev
- On GitHub Pages
- On IPFS for censorship resistance
- On any CDN

**Critical:** Must be served over HTTPS for WebRTC to work properly.

