## Post-Deployment Configuration

After deployment, you MUST update the signaling server URL:

**In `client/index.html`:**

Search for `const SIGNALING_SERVER` (in the JavaScript section near line 300):

```javascript
// Change this:
const SIGNALING_SERVER = 'ws://localhost:3000';

// To your deployed server:
const SIGNALING_SERVER = 'wss://your-domain.com';
// or
const SIGNALING_SERVER = 'wss://your-server-ip:3000';
```

